  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>主播 | 刘飞 潇磊</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>感谢</span><strong><span>影石 麦克风 Wave &amp; 摄像头 Link </span></strong><span>赞助播出</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_liBECyVctMczTF6uFjTlO-TRrHAb.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>即日起至 4 月 19 日，在影石天猫、京东官方旗舰店，报「半拿铁」可以领取购买 Link 和 Wave 的专属优惠券</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>——</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>当全球媒体机构还在固守人工编辑的工作流时，诞生于知春路民居的 APP 工厂，已经在准备创立一个没有编辑的时代。</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>本期节目，我们把时间拨回 2012 年。在移动互联网爆发的前夜，一个信奉延迟满足的程序员，是如何利用增长黑客和推荐算法，杀出重围的？又是如何通过流量倒换，在被国内主流投资人集体错过的至暗时刻，完成了对传统新闻分发模式的致命打击？</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>来杯半拿铁，咱们边喝边唠。</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>—</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>半拿铁也开始讲时事了：</span><a href=\"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/podcast/682c566cc7c5f17595635a2c\" data-url=\"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/podcast/682c566cc7c5f17595635a2c\"><span>半拿铁·周刊</span></a></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>半拿铁也开始讲故事了：</span><a href=\"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/podcast/66cf49c856bfd3907ac9250b\" data-url=\"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/podcast/66cf49c856bfd3907ac9250b\"><span>半拿铁·故事篇</span></a></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>📮听友投稿邮箱：bannatie@163.com</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>☕️杭州特调「芝麻·半拿铁」的品尝地：西湖区华星路 01coffee</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>👔半拿铁周边购买淘宝店：小羊商店Sheepedia</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>📖 半拿铁全新周边：《人工智能风云录》纸质书，可在各大电商平台购买。天猫店铺目前为 5 折</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>——</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>时间轴</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"358\">5:58</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;张一鸣的成长背景与早期教育</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"595\">9:55</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;高考志愿选择与大学经历</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"921\">15:21</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;早期技术探索与创业铺垫</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1216\">20:16</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;创业历程与九九房的发展</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"1879\">31:19</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;张一鸣的移动互联网洞察与产品创新</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"2249\">37:29</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;字节跳动的早期发展与未来构想</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"3199\">53:19</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;字节跳动的推荐系统逐渐成型。</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"3975\">1:06:15</a> &nbsp;今日头条的崛起与产品特色</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"4229\">1:10:29</a> &nbsp;张一鸣的至暗时刻与融资困境</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"4708\">1:18:28</a> &nbsp;今日头条广告系统与商业化发展</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"5282\">1:28:02</a> &nbsp;字节跳动的独特内容运营模式</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"5611\">1:33:31</a> &nbsp;头条与搜狐的版权大战</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"5721\">1:35:21</a> &nbsp;头条号生态的建立与行业变革</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"6430\">1:47:10</a> &nbsp;今日头条的监管与整改历程</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"7064\">1:57:44</a> &nbsp;字节跳动短视频产品的布局与挑战</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span><a class=\"timestamp\" data-timestamp=\"7937\">2:12:17</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;读评论</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>张一鸣长大的地方，龙岩市培丰镇积庆楼</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_FpVmJU-lmiLaZv_K7de7wt4XkRg_.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>酷讯老同事在 2016 年唱吧的聚会，能看到张一鸣</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_Fnp4fy0OWO1Fmy0_yxO8X3x2n1Kz.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>房产资讯 APP 的首页</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_FgNXfkWPquxGrnsxv0dvyakWjW0V.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_FjxhD8uVplrUKZjtK56FCbeHzSsK.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>年轻的张一鸣</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_FoO-N9UEbUCCE-qtPQ4MkG4K1Yq4.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>王琼回忆的张一鸣在餐巾纸上给她画的架构图</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_Fu86r9FWLB7ooG8_uaXH5eeP30ll.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>张一鸣知名的一条微博</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_FqMbpGHu6jwCzAG9Ow11qHwTxKnL.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>内涵段子时期，字节跳动的应用矩阵</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_FgBhCMnIowPgQcPrTR2eQ8ihMmjH.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>当年预装工厂的一角</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_FlGi0UdHmrDmrXfIMNnYJGl7zxQR.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_Fi1fHRZZzGWQA9wLCGXL-UwK0AtY.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>2013 年的字节员工合影</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_Fk_-UOGiUBMGWE1AjdojnBVbFdKl.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>朴素的招聘广告</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_Fn_c8hIcymJeiW-cda6ZPvVx2tk2.png\">\n  </figure>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>封面：张一鸣</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>主要参考资料：</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <ul>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>字节跳动，从0到1的秘密，马修·布伦南</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>大力出奇迹 : 张一鸣的创业心路与算法思维，王健平</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>沸腾新十年，林军，胡喆</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>解码酷讯创业帮：张一鸣这些80后老板们的“黄埔军校”，经济观察报</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>张一鸣：今日头条不模拟人性，也不引导人性，你们文化人给了我们太多深刻的命题，财经，小晚</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>张一鸣的第四次创业，乱翻书</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>杀死今日头条，品玩</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>让张一鸣“逃离”的微软，是程序员的天堂？，字母榜</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>今日头条融资故事：得到的和错过的，乱翻书</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>关于TikTok母公司字节跳动如何崛起，你应该知道的，纽约时报</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>张一鸣的投资帝国，中国企业家杂志</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>08年在酷讯和张一鸣成为同事，一些不为人知的故事，牟长青</span></li>\n   <span> </span>\n   <li><span>Gemini</span></li>\n   <span></span>\n  </ul>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>片尾曲：</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>北京北京 - 汪峰</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>本期制作人：</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>张超辉</span></p>\n  <span></span>\n  <p><span>——</span></p>\n  <span></span><span></span>\n  <figure>\n   <img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260122003353_FuNvrVng1jm2Mxt4k6t4X_qd7718.jpeg\">\n  </figure>\n </body>\n</html>",
